{"tid":2334587,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華相隔10年再出新數碼專輯《演‧唱》　盼藉歌聲治癒樂迷心情，帶出一點點的寧靜","createTime":"2020-12-21T09:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T12:29:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97647f5605b9d0d51373215448348daa68d2b085","tid":2334587,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"劉德華近日首度推出新數碼專輯《演‧唱》，是繼2010年《忘不了的》後再度推出個人專輯。合集一共收錄17首廣東和國語歌，包括近年的作品《My Love》、《繼續美麗》，及與倪妮合唱的電影《拆彈專家2》主題曲《相信我》。除了4首翻唱歌《誰能明白我》、《孤雁》、《浪子心聲》及《獅子山下》外，專輯內的其餘13首歌均由華仔親自填詞。<br />\n<br />\n在疫情下，華仔決定將新專輯改以數位版形式推出，讓歌迷更容易在網上收聽。他希望透過音樂，讓大家在此刻的氣氛下，藉歌聲治癒心情，帶出一點點的寧靜。新專輯在網上推出後，網民紛紛留言指自己已經期待已久，有部分歌迷知道專輯內大部份歌詞由華仔操刀後更直言：「在詞作中與華仔見字如見面！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201220/417445121445859328065317.jpeg/T0_lSDYiHUFkk_ICETfvo6eORMr1uOg57aQZ4O2kGeA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201220%2F417445121445859328065317.jpeg%2FT0_lSDYiHUFkk_ICETfvo6eORMr1uOg57aQZ4O2kGeA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=d9dff8c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3180199ce0379997a28f1fa6287d0a20784e3487","tid":2334587,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ae3bcc66078c5fcf655e19d5e0cdc25b4335d3a","tid":2334587,"uid":179409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"《填.海》"},{"pid":"ebaac73b2dbc510c3c6d1ac1d5cb8581b556ff32","tid":2334587,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"你毒啞自己 香港人咪寧靜囉"},{"pid":"57fd0a0495286f0e538844f4959ae0f38f6d29b0","tid":2334587,"uid":239321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ae3bcc66078c5fcf655e19d5e0cdc25b4335d3a","tid":2334587,"uid":179409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"《填.海》"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f